The ddrepeater is an app that will let your iPhone/iPad has the functions of repeater, It is specially designed for practising listening to a foreign language.

With ddrepeater ,you can set the times of repetitions for each sentence,the rate of playback and the pause time after each sentence, so that you can understand every sentence very carefully by automatic repeat play. 

In order to understand each sentence, ddrepeater provides some convenient operation modes. For example, when you long click a sentence, ddrepeater will automatically repeat this sentence. 

The repetitions of the listening and understanding every word carefully is the most effective way to learning a foreign language. 

Let’s use ddrepeater to listen every word.

Features:

1:Repetition of sentences one bye one;

2:Repetition between A and B;

3:Variable playback rate;

4:Audio waveform displaying;

5:Recording;

6:Adding sentences to favorite for review；

7:lyric Editor;

8:colorful UI and night mode;
